<div #greeting .panel>
  <div .panel-body>
    <p>
       Welcome, #{userEmail u}!  Thank you for signing up.

    <p>
      Before starting to use the site to full effect, you need to
      complete your profile.  Please select your defaults below.  This
      is so that you can use correct time stamps, units, and the such.

